OL,5, A woman who represented herself in     
OL,6, court using 80-year-old contract       
OL,7, legislation has beaten British Airways 
OL,8, (BA) in a row over flight vouchers.    
OL,10,FIn January 2020, Jennie Barber booked  
OL,11,Ftwo return flights to Japan departing  
OL,12,Fthat May, but the flights were later   
OL,13,Fpulled due to Covid restrictions.      
OL,15,FBA offered a refund in the form of     
OL,16,Ftravel vouchers but Ms Barber wanted   
OL,17,Fher money back. The airline refused.   
OL,19,FRepresenting herself, Ms Barber took BA
OL,20,Fto court and won a full refund.        
